name: Objkt #1-September 11
description: On September 11, 2001, the attack on the land of freedom took place. This is a great wound that will not be erased from the memories of recent history. This attack is one of the deadliest terrorist attacks in human history. As a result of this attack, hundreds of people were killed and thousands more injured. I respectfully commemorate the dozens of people who died with this work, and especially the firefighters who lost their lives.
